snippet.title: Svoboda 1945: Liberation Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Svoboda 1945: Liberation is a unique blend of adventure gameplay, full-motion video interviews with real actors and historically-accurate interactive memories of people who lived through the chaos of the aftermath of World War 2. 

Discover the secret history of your own family in a captivating story about reconciliation with the dark past. Releasing on 3rd of August for Mac and PC.

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1076620/Svoboda_1945_Liberation/
